sub_title: Design manager | Strategic designer | Founder & CEO at Design Jab | Challenging old thinking paradigms
summary:
Using a combination of critical thinking and rich imagination, I challenge every process, product, or idea that comes my way. I love creating innovative strategies for almost anything, obsessed with bringing real value to customers, and a champion of using the accurate data points and visuals to tell a well-constructed story. 

As a design leader, I inspire my teams to think differently and challenge the status quo. I believe that individual growth is key for team success, and therefore I focus on finding opportunities, removing blockers, coaching and mentoring team members. 

I bring with me strong leadership, communication, and facilitation skills together with vast experience in building, optimizing, and marketing products.
